data.description: Three bedroom, three full bath home for sale in Oak Park! Front & back porches for relaxing. Laminate wood floors and tile throughout, no carpet! Custom plantation shutters. Open floor plan for Living, Dining, & Kitchen. SS appliances & granite in kitchen. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet and spa like bathroom. Second bedroom comes with an attached bathroom. Spacious side/back yard for all your entertaining needs. Plenty of off street parking in driveway. Lakefront, Bayou St. John, and numerous entertainment options close by.
